node.text:
7 days of shooting/saving clips and 10 days of isolation. June was tough in its own way, still stoked with the amount I was able to get done. But it’s never enough 🤟😂🍅 July should be wild, let’s get it people ❤️🥳 feat. @tristanwrench 
•
#redbull #teamfarang #june #workhard

My very own rooftop POV shot with @storror member @benjcave 🥳🙏 We shot this with @redbull for the film ‘Twist’ in 2019 - unfortunately this segment didn’t make the final cut, but I was able to splice the shots together for you!! 
•
‘Twist’ will be coming to @readingcinemasau soon! So my Aussie pals 🇦🇺 hope you get a chance to see it ❤️🤟
•
#redbull #teamfarang #storror #pov #twist #london #throwbackthursday
